OL,3,CWary of complaining about your vet ?
OL,4,CHere's how to escalate concerns
OL,6,FNew research by Which? found that more
OL,7,Fthan a third of owners did not raise
OL,8,Fconcerns, because they did not want to
OL,9,Ffall out with their vet, while 16% did
OL,10,Fnot know how to complain.
OL,12,FIt also showed that more than 50% of
OL,13,Fpet owners consider the price of vet
OL,14,Fcare was excessive, despite just less
OL,15,Fthan a quarter saying they have issues
OL,16,Fwith the quality of care.
OL,18,FHow can pet owners escalate
OL,19,Fcomplaints? ITV News explains.
