OL,3,CWary of complaining about your vet ?
OL,4,CHere's how to escalate concerns
OL,6,FAccording to Lisa Webb, a legal expert
OL,7,Fat Which?, pet owners are protected
OL,8,Funder the law.
OL,10,FIf a vet has acted negligently, pet
OL,11,Fowners can seek compensation or
OL,12,Fdamages from the veterinary practice,
OL,13,FWebb said.
OL,15,FUnder the Consumer Rights Act, vets
OL,16,Fhave a duty to provide a "service with
OL,17,Freasonable care and skills", according
OL,18,Fto Which?
