OL,3,CWary of complaining about your vet ?
OL,4,CHere's how to escalate concerns
OL,6,FIf you are unhappy with the service
OL,7,Fprovided, Which? says you can either
OL,8,Fcomplain to the practice directly or
OL,9,Frequest a remedy under the Consumer
OL,10,FRights Act.
OL,12,FThis could include redoing part or all
OL,13,Fof the service at no extra cost, or
OL,14,Fagreeing to a price reduction or
OL,15,Frefund.
OL,17,FHow can you complain to the practice?
OL,19,FWhich? advises that customers should
OL,20,Ffirst speak to the practice about
OL,21,Ftheir complaint.
